Oh Vaishnava ! Oh Vaishnava , Krishna Tava Krishna Tava 
Ami Tomar Krishnera Dasanu Daas

Ami Paapi Aparaadhi , Stri Sangi aar Maayaavaadi 
Mora Gati Tomara Charane Paash 

Kabe Sei Dina Amaar , Netre bahe Krishna-ashru dhaar 
Aparadhe ami haya shudhhha

Sei dina Mulyavaana , Oh Vaishnava more koro daana 
Tabe na rahe mora indriya kshubdha 


Vaishnavera Kripa Saar , ek Maatra Aashaa aamaar 
Tabe janme lesh maatra Guna 

Vaishnavera Charana Dhuli , Dine Dine Snaan kori 
Tabe Mora Jivana maani Purna 


Mor Aparadhera Varnana , Naahi Taar gaṅana 
Nirapradh Naam haya Asambhava 

Ratri Dine Naam Gaimu , Janme Janme Prem Na Paimu 
Vina Mahat Pāda Rajera Stava 


Vaishnavera Guna Gaan , ami Aparadhire Diye Sammaan 
Sei Vaishnava Gaan mora Maṅī

Janme Janme Ek Aasha , Jihvaa kare Gaan Sadaa 
Shareera naache Vaishnavera Vaani














